headline.main: Tottenham and Man City Keep Up the Chase
headline.print_headline: Tottenham and Man City Keep Up the Chase

lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur and Manchester City both issued timely reminders to Chelsea that the Premier League title race might not be over with impressive victories on Sunday.
